title: #254: Spoiler Alert 5 - Zoolander No. 2 (@Kathleen_McGee)
itunes:title: Spoiler Alert 5: Zoolander No. 2 with Kathleen McGee
description: Kathleen McGee and I went to see Zoolander no. 2 in Vancouver and we did a spoiler alert podcast about it. Its the 2nd year in a road we did this. And both times with sequels. It's a fun discussion about the movie and also a drug and injury fueled trip to Whistler.
